# Aradhana Monorepo Environment Variables Template
#
# This project contains separate environment configurations for the backend and frontend.
# Please refer to the respective subfolders for instructions:
#
# - Backend configuration: backend/.env.example
# - Frontend configuration: frontend/.env.example
#
# For production deployment (e.g. Render), configure these variables directly in the
# Render dashboard for each service, or use the Blueprint variables in render.yaml.
